// ─────────────── Programme & Scheme (Part 6 / Part 13) ───────────────
// One reusable programme/scheme record. TRIMMED (scope discipline): the `toolkits`,
// `procurementUpdates`, and `enquiries` back-relations from Part 13 are OMITTED (those modules
// are out of Phase 6 scope) and re-added additively later (Tiers 9/12/13).
model ProgrammeScheme {
